  <description><![CDATA[<p>The superb ski-inclusive hotel has everything that you need for a week’s skiing included in the holiday price; a 6 day lift pass, skis or snowboard and boots, full board including wine, children’s clubs, evening entertainment and much more (see below). It is located in <strong>Les Menuires</strong> on the side of the piste providing very easy access into the fabulous <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valley ski area</a>. The local swimming pool with wellness area is only a short walk away.</p>
<p>Your Ski Inclusive Holiday includes:</p>
<p><strong>Free</strong> 6 day Three Valleys lift pass</p>
<p><strong>Free</strong> rental of skis or snowboard</p>
<p><strong>Free</strong> ski/board boot rental (supplement for superior skis or mini skis)</p>
<p><strong>Free</strong> helmet rental for children</p>
<p><strong>Free</strong> lunches or picnics</p>
<p><strong>Free</strong> wine with dinner</p>
<p><strong>Free</strong> evening entertainment and cabarets</p>
<p><strong>Free</strong> children’s clubs</p>
<p><strong>Free</strong> half day adult ski hosting with the ski school</p>
<p><strong>Free</strong> snowshoe outing</p>]]></description>
