  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<p>Families: Mini Clubs for children including Câlins (3mths -1yr), Coquins (2-3yrs) and Malins (4-5yrs), open Sunday-Friday from 8.30am-6pm and 7pm-9pm with a full programme of indoor and outdoor activities. Malins also includes lessons in the Jardin de Neiges. Children dine with the activity leader for lunch and parents in the evenings. Children's club Copains (6-10 yrs) is open afternoons all season and full days 21 Dec-3 Jan and 15 Feb-14 Mar. The Club Jeune (11-17 yrs) is open full days 21 Dec-3 Jan and 15 Feb-14 Mar. It includes pick up and drop off to ski school meeting place if required (lessons not included). See our Families page in the header above for more information on children.</p>]]></familyDescription>
